# /handle-cancellation
# Usage: claude /handle-cancellation --client "Maria G." --reason "no-show"
# Handles appointment cancellation dynamically.

When a client cancels or no-shows:
1. Mark the appointment as cancelled in the calendar
2. Record the reason (no_show, client_request, broker_request, force_majeure)
3. Re-optimize the remaining route from broker's current location
4. Query nearby qualified leads from property database
5. Draft WhatsApp messages to propose new meetings
6. Present options to broker for approval
7. If no suitable alternatives found, suggest admin tasks or early wrap

Use the handle-cancellation skill. All outbound messages require broker approval via "yes" / "enviar" / "ok".
